evcon
------------------------------------------
evcon is a generic wrapper library that sits between libraries that need
socket (file descriptor), timeout and (thread safe) asynchronous events, and
an application that wants to use the library.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.4-1
  libev4-4.33-1
  libevcon-devel-0.1.0+git20121105-1bl1
  libevcon-ev-devel-0.1.0+git20121105-1bl1
  libevcon-ev0-0.1.0+git20121105-1bl1
  libevcon-event-devel-0.1.0+git20121105-1bl1
  libevcon-event0-0.1.0+git20121105-1bl1
  libevcon-glib-devel-0.1.0+git20121105-1bl1
  libevcon-glib0-0.1.0+git20121105-1bl1
  libevcon0-0.1.0+git20121105-1bl1
  libevent2.1_7-2.1.12-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.85.2-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-2
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.45-1
  cygport-0.37.2-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  libev-devel-4.33-1
  libevent-devel-2.1.12-1
  libglib2.0-devel-2.85.2-1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/lighttpd/evcon

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/lighttpd/evcon.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack evcon-0.1.0+git20121105-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./evcon-0.1.0+git20121105-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/evcon-0.1.0+git20121105-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/evcon-0.1.0+git20121105-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libevcon0-0.1.0+git20121105-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libevcon-devel-0.1.0+git20121105-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libevcon-ev0-0.1.0+git20121105-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libevcon-ev-devel-0.1.0+git20121105-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libevcon-event0-0.1.0+git20121105-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libevcon-event-devel-0.1.0+git20121105-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libevcon-glib0-0.1.0+git20121105-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libevcon-glib-devel-0.1.0+git20121105-X.tar.xz

